text: Vikram Malhotra (born 16 November 1989 in Mumbai) is an Indian professional squash player. As of February 2018, he was ranked number 68 in the world. ==References== Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:Indian male squash players Category:Trinity Bantams men's squash players Category:Squash players at the 2018 Commonwealth Games Category:Commonwealth Games competitors for India
